      "id": "3f85a51c-e286-9f44-b4dc-51d00768696c",
      "text": "Enable Predictive autoscale and configure at least for Forecast Only",
      "description": "Predictive autoscale utilizes machine learning to efficiently manage and scale Azure Virtual Machine Scale Sets by forecasting CPU load through historical usage analysis, ensuring timely scale-out to meet demand.",
